metadata.name: Gremlin 1
metadata.description: A Gremlin is a mythological creature similar to a fairy or goblin which originated during the World War, said to cause havoc everywhere they went. Gremlin society consists of a large number of tribes which display little to no loyalty to each other. These groups have a general hierarchy, which usually consists of the biggest and toughest Gremlin exerting itâ€™s authority over the others, Located in the metaverse you can find 10 000 cute, but scary Gremlins causing havoc and trying to take over the ETH blockchain.
